mca:evidence-live-auction-2009 crm:P104_is_subject_to _:b0_r7b0;
    crm:P129_is_about mca:auction-as-artwork, mca:production-live-auction-2009, mca:sothebys-photographs-auction-2009, mca:wtf-is-ansel-adams, mca:wtfisart;
    crm:P190_has_symbolic_content "Sun & Rain Works holds a private archive relating to its 2009 engagement with Sotheby's Photographs (sale N08533) and the associated conceptual works (The Auction as Artwork, WTF is Ansel Adams, and www.wtfisart.com). The archive is reported to contain 2008 correspondence with Sotheby's (outbound and inbound), records of the consignment of an Ansel Adams photograph, 'San Francisco from Twin Peaks' (lot 16), domain-registration and hosting receipts for www.wtfisart.com naming Sun & Rain Works, art-referential documentation photographs, and file metadata. These materials evidence the artist identity, the 2008-2009 engagement with Sotheby's, the consignment, contemporaneous conceptual intent, and the public continuity of the 'WTF is Art' concept. They do not, by themselves, record a publicly witnessed live-creation event, and they establish no precedence over any later event. The fuller archive remains held by the studio pending redaction and rights review; no checksums, file hashes, or custody identifiers are published at this time.";
    crm:P1_is_identified_by _:b0_r7b1, _:b0_r7b2;
    crm:P2_has_type aat:300026087, aat:300026906;
    crm:P67i_is_referred_to_by _:b0_r7b3, _:b0_r7b4;
    crm:P94i_was_created_by _:b0_r7b5;
    a crm:E33_Linguistic_Object;
    rdfs:label "Evidence archive: Sun & Rain Works auction engagement (2009)";
    la:member_of mca:collection.
