_:b0_r18b3 crm:P190_has_symbolic_content "work:wtfisart";
    crm:P2_has_type aat:300312355;
    a crm:E42_Identifier.
_:b0_r18b4 crm:P190_has_symbolic_content "https://www.wtfisart.com/";
    crm:P2_has_type aat:300404626;
    a crm:E42_Identifier.
_:b0_r18b5 crm:P190_has_symbolic_content "A born-digital Metaconceptual Art work: a website built and owned by Sun & Rain Works around 2009, in connection with its Sotheby's Photographs auction engagement (sale N08533). Sun & Rain Works designates it as an associated part of the conceptual work The Auction as Artwork.";
    crm:P2_has_type aat:300435416;
    a crm:E33_Linguistic_Object.
_:b0_r18b6 crm:P190_has_symbolic_content "www.wtfisart.com is associated by Sun & Rain Works with the conceptual work The Auction as Artwork, in which Sun & Rain Works designates its 2009 Sotheby's Photographs auction engagement as art. The designation is an assertion by the artist.";
    crm:P2_has_type aat:300435416;
    a crm:E33_Linguistic_Object.
_:b0_r18b7 crm:P190_has_symbolic_content "Sun & Rain Works reports domain-registration and hosting receipts, site metadata, and related records documenting the website's existence and date. The fuller archive remains held by the studio pending redaction and rights review.";
    crm:P2_has_type aat:300435416;
    a crm:E33_Linguistic_Object.
